Helix 2025 - Ultimate Shortcut Reference (April 2025)
======================================================

üìÇ Basic File Management

| Action | Keybinding | Description |
|:---|:---|:---|
| Open File Picker | Space + f | Fuzzy find and open files |
| Create Scratch Buffer | :new or :n | Open a new temporary file buffer |
| List Open Buffers | Space + b | List of opened files (buffer picker) |
| Next Buffer | g n | Switch to next buffer |
| Previous Buffer | g p | Switch to previous buffer |
| Close Current Buffer | :buffer-close or :bc | Close the currently open file |
| Close Others | :buffer-close-others or :bco | Keep only current buffer |

------------------------------------------------------

üîé Navigation and Code Roaming

| Action | Keybinding | Description |
|:---|:---|:---|
| Open Symbol Picker (functions/classes) | Space + s | Fuzzy search symbols and jump |
| Go to Definition | g d | Jump directly to a symbol definition (needs LSP) |
| Find References (usages) | g r | List all places a symbol is used |
| Save Jump Location | Ctrl + s | Save current spot into jump list |
| Open Jump List | Space + j | Open saved jump locations |
| Search Project (ripgrep) | Space + / | Search across project (needs rg installed) |

